until two games ago. He re-injured himself in Sunday's victory at 
Minnesota. 
</P>
<P>
	Boniol kicked for both Philadelphia and Cleveland in training  
camp this summer. The last two seasons, he kicked for the Eagles, 
the Bears' opponent this Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
	With Dallas, he hit 27 of 28 field goal attempts in 1995. In  
five years in the NFL, he has made 117 of his 145 field goal 
attempts (.807). 
  	   	
